1
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:37,240
BASED ON THE JJWXC NOVEL
WHEN DESTINY BRINGS THE DEMON BY FU HUA

2
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:38,680
EPISODE 19

3
00:01:38,760 --> 00:01:40,480
IMMORTAL AND DEMON ON SEPARATE PATHS,
PARTED BY LIFE AND DEATH

4
00:01:41,080 --> 00:01:43,800
TAIWEI MOUNTAIN

5
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,640
That's a powerful barrier.

6
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:49,840
The Spirit Fire must be inside.

7
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,040
A Bloodmist Array.

8
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:20,040
A pool filled with
the blood of the Fengshan Clan.

9
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:40,360
You are but a guard dog.

10
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:47,960
Promise me. Don't tear open your wounds

11
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:51,040
or bump into anything,
or I will be heartbroken.

12
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,520
Come in.

13
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:43,040
Who are you?

14
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:45,280
Jiao,

15
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:48,960
come in, and I will tell you.

16
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:59,680
BLACK JADE LOTUS POND

17
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,280
The Spirit Fire

18
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,400
really is here.

19
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:33,000
Jiao,

20
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:34,960
you've finally come.

21
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:37,160
Are you Sima Shi?

22
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:39,480
I've been waiting for you.

23
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:43,080
So you didn't die in
the fire at White Deer Cliff.

24
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:46,680
So E did as I asked

25
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:49,440
and merged the Spirit Fire with you.

26
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:53,880
I am so glad that you managed
to pull through.

27
00:05:58,440 --> 00:06:01,200
- I'll get you out of here.
- Don't bother.

28
00:06:01,280 --> 00:06:02,920
I didn't wait for you

29
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,600
because I wanted to leave.

30
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:09,120
With this broken body of mine,

31
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:11,520
I could never leave again.

32
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:14,400
I lingered here, waiting,

33
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:16,080
just to tell you

34
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:18,240
what really happened back then.

35
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:21,640
The ascension curse

36
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:25,320
made the Sima clan dwindle further.

37
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:27,240
We, despite our precious blood,

38
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:29,280
fell from leaders

39
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:32,320
to mere tools of the Eight Palaces.

40
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,600
By my generation,

41
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:38,680
all freedom had been lost.

42
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:40,520
To produce

43
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:43,760
a more refined Fengshan
bloodline to nourish the Spirit Fire,

44
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:47,320
the Eight Palaces forced
your mother and me into marriage.

45
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,280
Soon after,

46
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,080
you,

47
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:55,920
with the purest Fengshan atavistic blood,
were born.

48
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:59,480
Seeing such purity,

49
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:02,200
the greed of the Eight Palaces

50
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,360
grew insatiable.

51
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:07,440
They wanted more
offspring of this bloodline,

52
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:10,240
so they sealed
your mother and me in White Deer Cliff.

53
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:13,520
The Sima clan must
remain here to guard the Spirit Fire.

54
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:16,800
Grandmaster,
please stay on White Deer Cliff.

55
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:19,360
You are treating us like prisoners!

56
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:22,280
Do you even have
the slightest respect for us Grandmasters?

57
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,760
I had intended to merge
with the Fengshan Spirit Fire

58
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:30,920
so that I could gain its power

59
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:34,000
and put an end to their scheme.

60
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:36,400
But the Spirit Fire was too powerful.

61
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:39,360
I could not endure the agony

62
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:42,960
and even fell into madness at one point.

63
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:45,880
In the end,

64
00:07:47,200 --> 00:07:48,360
I had to give up.

65
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,680
And even knowing the pain,

66
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:57,560
you still chose to have
me merge with the Spirit Fire?

67
00:07:57,640 --> 00:08:00,840
I… I had no other choice.

68
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:04,680
With your rare and pure
Fengshan atavistic blood,

69
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:06,240
you could withstand the Spirit Fire

70
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:09,640
and become the first to
break the ascension curse.

71
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,640
But during the fusion, we realized

72
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:15,360
that your blood was so pure

73
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,800
that you needed
a stronger Spirit Fire to merge with.

74
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,080
Otherwise,

75
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:23,760
your blood would devour

76
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:26,400
the Spirit Fire
entirely during the fusion.

77
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:28,160
So,

78
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:31,120
the other Sima clansmen and I

79
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:34,440
made a collective decision.

80
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:36,039
If our deaths

81
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:38,280
can help Jiao
successfully merge with the Spirit Fire,

82
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,360
then the Eight Palaces will no longer

83
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:41,880
- dare to harm the Sima clan!
- That's right!

84
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,280
We're willing to help
Jiao merge with the Spirit Fire!

85
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:45,240
- Me too!
- Yes, me too!

86
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:47,760
- Me too!
- I'm in!

87
00:08:48,760 --> 00:08:51,280
The Sima clan no longer
allowed themselves to be pawns

88
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:53,680
for the greed of the Eight Palaces.

89
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:58,760
So we decided to feed
the Spirit Fire with our blood

90
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,800
to form a Spirit Fire strong enough

91
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:03,400
for you to merge with.

92
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:04,760
But

93
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,960
once the blood sacrifice began,

94
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:12,120
we found that the Spirit Fire
was like a bottomless pit.

95
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:18,800
Over 100 clansmen gave
their lives one after another.

96
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:21,440
Not a single one gave up.

97
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:23,680
In the end,

98
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:28,160
the clansmen poured
every drop of their blood into it

99
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:33,520
and finally formed the most
powerful Spirit Fire in existence.

100
00:09:35,280 --> 00:09:37,320
Sacrificing the entire clan

101
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:43,480
and leaving such
a heavy burden on a child…

102
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:46,680
Should I call you pitiable, or despicable?

103
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:49,040
If we had to choose again,

104
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:52,240
we would still walk the same path.

105
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:03,440
Then why are you here?

106
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:06,800
I feared the Eight Palaces
would figure out our plan,

107
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:09,760
so I feigned madness and set a fire,

108
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:13,200
making them believe I had gone insane

109
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:15,080
and burned the whole clan alive.

110
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:18,200
The final step for
merging the Spirit Fire into you

111
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:24,360
required your mother to absorb it for you.

112
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:27,640
I thought our plan

113
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:30,240
would end there.

114
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,400
He's dead.

115
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:46,320
Oh, no. Where is Sima E?

116
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:48,760
- Hurry!
- But in the fire at White Deer Cliff,

117
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:51,560
a spy the Shi family had
planted in the Eight Palaces

118
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:53,960
found me, barely alive,

119
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:58,560
and secretly took me away.

120
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:01,560
At first, the Shi family
truly meant to save me.

121
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:04,400
But once I was rescued,
I was desperate to find you,

122
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:07,680
and from me, Shi Yongyou learned

123
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:09,560
the secret of how to
break the ascension curse.

124
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:12,960
That greed consumed him.

125
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:16,480
Shi Yongyou and his disciple, Shi Qianlv,

126
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:19,640
stole a dying flame
of the Spirit Fire's avatar

127
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:21,400
from White Deer Cliff

128
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:25,640
and used my body as
the wick to keep it alive,

129
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,680
and at the same time…

130
00:11:28,280 --> 00:11:29,200
At the same time,

131
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:34,720
Shi Yongyou and Shi Qianlv
secretly built Baifeng Mountain,

132
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,640
gathering the blood of the Fengshan Clan

133
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:39,120
to feed that Spirit Fire.

134
00:11:40,760 --> 00:11:41,680
Exactly.

135
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:45,120
Now that you've come here,

136
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:47,520
it is time for all of this to end.

137
00:11:48,640 --> 00:11:50,880
Jiao, remember this.

138
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:52,640
We are the Fengshan Clan.

139
00:11:53,560 --> 00:11:56,440
The Fengshan Clan is born extraordinary,

140
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:59,520
destined to share life
with heaven and earth.

141
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:01,160
Share life with heaven and earth?

142
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,080
Look around you.

143
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:06,560
Now the Sima clan

144
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,440
has only me left.

145
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:11,480
So what if there is only you left?

146
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:13,920
As long as you can
live for tens of thousands

147
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:15,680
of years,

148
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:17,040
as long as you don't die,

149
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:19,720
the Fengshan Clan will never vanish,

150
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:23,480
and the glory may one day be ours again.

151
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:26,120
Consume this Spirit Fire,

152
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:28,160
and not only will your wounds heal,

153
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:33,400
but you will also have
two Spirit Fires inside you.

154
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:38,160
But beyond becoming stronger,

155
00:12:39,640 --> 00:12:40,680
there is another possibility.

156
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:43,280
If I consume it,

157
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,920
the Spirit Fire might
reduce me to ash in an instant.

158
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:50,840
Isn't that right?

159
00:12:51,680 --> 00:12:54,840
You carry the atavistic Fengshan
bloodline, a marvel unseen in ages.

160
00:12:56,720 --> 00:13:01,040
You can accomplish
what none of us ever could.

161
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:10,680
Now your wish is fulfilled.

162
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:28,640
There's trouble

163
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:30,840
at Taiwei Mountain.

164
00:14:30,920 --> 00:14:34,040
Sect Master, Madam Ye sent word that
Liao Tingyan had been found.

165
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:39,440
Order Ye Ruling to seize
her and bring her to Taixuan Peak at once.

166
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:42,680
Otherwise, all
her clansmen at the Yin Palace will die.

167
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,280
Understood.

168
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:48,960
I can sense that something

169
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,720
has happened to
the Spirit Fire at Taiwei Mountain.

170
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:55,080
Sima Jiao may have already found it.

171
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:57,920
I'll go there first to check.

172
00:14:58,000 --> 00:15:00,280
Notify the palace
heads to gather at Taixuan Peak

173
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,480
and set up an array.

174
00:15:01,560 --> 00:15:04,400
Once Sima Jiao shows
himself at Taiwei Mountain,

175
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:06,640
I will use Liao Tingyan

176
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:07,920
to draw him to Taixuan Peak.

177
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:11,000
Then, the palace heads

178
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:12,360
will capture him together.

179
00:15:13,040 --> 00:15:13,880
Understood.

180
00:15:30,560 --> 00:15:33,320
Could this mean something unexpected
will happen to Sima Jiao?

181
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:40,800
What kind of fool curses
her own cultivation partner?

182
00:15:42,160 --> 00:15:43,240
He's so powerful.

183
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:46,000
No one in this world could kill him.

184
00:15:47,760 --> 00:15:49,360
He might suffer a small injury,

185
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:51,160
but nothing serious will happen.

186
00:15:52,280 --> 00:15:54,240
If only I still had
the Transvision Mirror.

187
00:15:55,640 --> 00:15:57,560
Then Jiao would be
able to tell me he's safe.

188
00:15:57,640 --> 00:15:58,680
Ruling!

189
00:15:59,560 --> 00:16:00,400
Nianjiu?

190
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:06,480
Ruling!

191
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,120
Ruling!

192
00:16:09,520 --> 00:16:10,360
Nianjiu!

193
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:13,360
Tingyan! Tingyan!

194
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:14,600
Capture her!

195
00:16:22,280 --> 00:16:23,120
Madam Ye,

196
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:26,080
I didn't expect us to meet again so soon.

197
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,280
How did you even find me?

198
00:16:29,400 --> 00:16:30,680
In the Immortal Realm,

199
00:16:30,760 --> 00:16:32,360
only I can recognize
the traces of your extreme-cold nature.

200
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:34,280
Your cultivation has
advanced rapidly lately,

201
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:37,080
and the traces have
become clearer than ever.

202
00:16:37,880 --> 00:16:40,840
So I should thank you for
not coming to capture me sooner?

203
00:16:44,520 --> 00:16:45,400
The Sect Master said

204
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:49,120
that if we could not catch Sima Jiao,
we must at least bring Liao Tingyan back.

205
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:57,320
Tingyan! Tingyan!

206
00:16:57,400 --> 00:16:58,640
You're courting death!

207
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:04,160
Madam Ye, whose side are you really on?

208
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:06,920
How dare you,
a mere disciple, question me?

209
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:10,200
Yes, Sect Master Shi
ordered you to watch me,

210
00:17:10,839 --> 00:17:12,119
but he didn't tell you to command me,

211
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:16,520
and I certainly don't need
to explain my decisions to you.

212
00:17:17,319 --> 00:17:18,319
Let's get back to business.

213
00:17:19,359 --> 00:17:20,400
Take her away!

214
00:17:21,640 --> 00:17:23,520
- Move.
- Let her go!

215
00:17:24,040 --> 00:17:26,000
Tingyan! Tingyan!

216
00:17:26,599 --> 00:17:27,720
Let me out!

217
00:17:29,800 --> 00:17:30,960
Ruling!

218
00:17:31,600 --> 00:17:34,040
Let Tingyan go! Ruling!

219
00:17:42,520 --> 00:17:43,560
My Spirit Fire…

220
00:17:58,240 --> 00:17:59,440
You are finally here.

221
00:18:00,160 --> 00:18:01,840
You absorbed my Spirit Fire!

222
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:04,280
Centuries of planning, and you walked away

223
00:18:04,360 --> 00:18:05,680
with the prize.

224
00:18:06,520 --> 00:18:07,520
Sima Jiao,

225
00:18:08,320 --> 00:18:10,840
you vile, despicable man!

226
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:12,200
I am flattered.

227
00:18:23,600 --> 00:18:26,720
TAIXUAN PEAK

228
00:18:33,960 --> 00:18:35,200
Sima Jiao harmed my daughter,

229
00:18:36,280 --> 00:18:38,120
causing me endless pain.

230
00:18:38,920 --> 00:18:42,720
Now, I'll make him taste the same.

231
00:18:53,040 --> 00:18:53,880
How can this be?

232
00:18:56,960 --> 00:18:59,080
She has such powerful defenses.

233
00:19:00,080 --> 00:19:02,800
- I can't wound her at all.
- Madam Yue,

234
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:05,000
we're against a strong enemy.
Don't act rashly.

235
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:08,240
Madam Yue, if anyone here

236
00:19:08,320 --> 00:19:10,880
destroys this tool
meant for the capture of Sima Jiao,

237
00:19:10,960 --> 00:19:14,040
I will have to treat them as a saboteur
of the Eight Palaces' grand plan.

238
00:19:14,120 --> 00:19:17,280
Ye Ruling, whose side are you really on?

239
00:19:19,080 --> 00:19:22,600
Even now, you still have
sympathy for Liao Tingyan, don't you?

240
00:19:23,600 --> 00:19:26,200
Madam Yue, now is not
the time for personal grudges.

241
00:19:26,280 --> 00:19:27,480
We must focus on our task.

242
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:29,560
Master Ri is right.

243
00:19:30,160 --> 00:19:32,760
Fellow palace heads,
there is no time to waste.

244
00:19:32,840 --> 00:19:33,680
Let's form the array.

245
00:19:48,120 --> 00:19:50,160
Please notify Sect Master Shi at once
that Liao is in place,

246
00:19:50,240 --> 00:19:52,440
and tell him to hurry and
lead Sima Jiao to Taixuan Peak.

247
00:20:24,080 --> 00:20:25,880
Qianlv, Madam Ye did it!

248
00:21:02,520 --> 00:21:03,640
No!

249
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:05,240
No!

250
00:21:05,840 --> 00:21:09,680
My… my Black Jade Lotus Pond!

251
00:21:09,760 --> 00:21:12,800
A blood pool made from
the blood of the Sima clan

252
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:15,520
will also be destroyed
by the blood of the Sima clan.

253
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:17,240
Shi Qianlv,

254
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:20,480
this is only the beginning.

255
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:27,200
What are you trying to do?

256
00:21:31,840 --> 00:21:32,680
Listen.

257
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:13,240
What's happening?

258
00:22:14,560 --> 00:22:15,520
The spirit veins are burning!

259
00:22:16,240 --> 00:22:18,960
Disciples of the Moon Palace,
move away from the veins at once!

260
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:25,960
Spirit veins burning?

261
00:22:26,560 --> 00:22:27,480
That must be Sima Jiao.

262
00:22:28,120 --> 00:22:29,560
I wonder how he is holding up.

263
00:22:32,080 --> 00:22:34,040
Liao Tingyan must not be spared!

264
00:22:34,120 --> 00:22:35,840
We don't have time. We must leave now!

265
00:22:43,360 --> 00:22:46,880
The Shi clan's spiritual peaks, temples,

266
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:48,640
and tombs,

267
00:22:48,720 --> 00:22:50,760
and even your Taixuan Peak,

268
00:22:51,600 --> 00:22:53,640
will all be engulfed in fire.

269
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:56,040
From this day forward,

270
00:22:56,120 --> 00:22:57,960
your entire clan

271
00:22:58,040 --> 00:23:01,640
and every spiritual
peak you own will be gone.

272
00:23:03,120 --> 00:23:04,040
Shi Qianlv,

273
00:23:05,240 --> 00:23:07,840
how does it feel to see
everything you worked for

274
00:23:08,760 --> 00:23:10,000
reduced to ash?

275
00:23:12,160 --> 00:23:13,360
Sima Jiao,

276
00:23:14,120 --> 00:23:16,160
you've been planning this all along.

277
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:21,920
You will regret it!

278
00:23:57,760 --> 00:24:00,120
Tingyan, get up. Go now.

279
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:03,280
- Why are you saving me?
- I told you I never wished to harm you.

280
00:24:03,960 --> 00:24:05,640
- Go.
- Let's leave together.

281
00:24:05,720 --> 00:24:06,720
I can't.

282
00:24:07,240 --> 00:24:10,520
In order to manipulate me,
Shi Qianlv brought my clansmen here.

283
00:24:11,240 --> 00:24:12,640
I must stay with them.

284
00:24:14,400 --> 00:24:15,320
Look out!

285
00:24:19,920 --> 00:24:21,120
There's no way out.

286
00:24:56,240 --> 00:24:57,080
Sima Jiao,

287
00:24:57,680 --> 00:25:00,480
you think you've won, but hear this:

288
00:25:01,800 --> 00:25:03,920
the woman you keep by your side

289
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:06,760
is also on Taixuan Peak.

290
00:25:10,400 --> 00:25:14,360
If we die, she will die with us!

291
00:25:16,560 --> 00:25:17,520
What did you say?

292
00:25:19,680 --> 00:25:21,000
You schemed and schemed,

293
00:25:21,800 --> 00:25:22,800
yet you never foresaw

294
00:25:23,600 --> 00:25:25,880
you would be the one to kill
the person you care for most, right?

295
00:25:27,160 --> 00:25:28,240
How does that feel?

296
00:25:28,320 --> 00:25:32,040
Your arrogance has
brought you retribution!

297
00:26:08,240 --> 00:26:09,600
Watch out!

298
00:26:23,040 --> 00:26:24,520
Sima Jiao,

299
00:26:25,560 --> 00:26:30,680
this time, I can't wait
for you to come home.

300
00:27:00,920 --> 00:27:01,840
Tingyan.

301
00:27:03,560 --> 00:27:05,360
Tingyan. Tingyan.

302
00:27:11,120 --> 00:27:12,040
Tingyan.

303
00:27:15,680 --> 00:27:16,520
Tingyan!

304
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:18,280
Tingyan…

305
00:27:37,520 --> 00:27:39,480
The artifact couldn't
withstand my Spirit Fire…

306
00:28:11,800 --> 00:28:13,560
Why can't I find you?

307
00:28:14,440 --> 00:28:15,800
Why can't I find you?

308
00:28:17,240 --> 00:28:18,480
Why can't I…?

309
00:28:35,520 --> 00:28:37,240
Your soul must still be here.

310
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:42,360
I will find it.

311
00:29:24,160 --> 00:29:25,480
Grandmaster!

312
00:29:25,560 --> 00:29:27,840
Grandmaster! Grandmaster.

313
00:29:29,280 --> 00:29:31,160
Have you found Tingyan's soul fragments?

314
00:29:38,560 --> 00:29:43,080
Grandmaster, you've
searched the entire Celestial Palace,

315
00:29:44,080 --> 00:29:45,720
but there is still no trace of her soul.

316
00:29:47,600 --> 00:29:49,360
- Perhaps she really is…
- She's not dead.

317
00:29:51,840 --> 00:29:52,880
She cannot be dead.

318
00:29:54,160 --> 00:29:55,560
Grandmaster…

319
00:29:56,160 --> 00:29:57,440
The two Spirit Fires in your body

320
00:29:57,520 --> 00:29:58,840
haven't fully merged yet.

321
00:29:58,920 --> 00:30:00,320
If you keep this up,

322
00:30:00,400 --> 00:30:01,480
you'll be in danger.

323
00:30:03,520 --> 00:30:05,080
- Keep looking for her.
- Grandmaster…

324
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:06,080
Grandmaster!

325
00:30:06,680 --> 00:30:07,720
Grandmaster!

326
00:30:08,520 --> 00:30:10,240
Grandmaster… Grandmaster!

327
00:30:12,880 --> 00:30:13,840
Grandmaster!

328
00:30:20,040 --> 00:30:22,320
That battle at Taiwei Mountain

329
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:23,240
EIGHTEEN YEARS LATER

330
00:30:23,320 --> 00:30:26,440
shattered the spirit veins
and toppled the Celestial Palace.

331
00:30:26,960 --> 00:30:31,120
After the Lord of Mercy lost his
cultivation partner, his spirit collapsed,

332
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:34,440
and he gave in to inner
demons, never waking again.

333
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:39,760
Just then, the Immortal-Demon Barrier
cracked, and demons broke in.

334
00:30:40,280 --> 00:30:43,280
The Gengchen Celestial Palace
was on the brink of destruction.

335
00:31:02,400 --> 00:31:04,920
Anhe, we can't hold out much longer.

336
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:07,120
Take the men back and fortify the defenses

337
00:31:07,200 --> 00:31:08,040
to protect the Grandmaster.

338
00:31:08,120 --> 00:31:10,440
- What about you, Nianjiu?
- I can still hold out a little longer.

339
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:12,400
Go!

340
00:31:30,800 --> 00:31:32,840
You Chi, the Demon Lord,
and his Preceptor, Mingli,

341
00:31:32,920 --> 00:31:34,720
recently seized another city.

342
00:31:34,800 --> 00:31:36,320
If the Grandmaster doesn't wake soon,

343
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:38,120
the Celestial Palace might really fall.

344
00:31:39,600 --> 00:31:42,120
Who would have thought
that a place once so glorious

345
00:31:42,200 --> 00:31:44,200
would end up like this?

346
00:31:44,280 --> 00:31:45,680
If only the Grandmaster were awake.

347
00:31:45,760 --> 00:31:46,920
Yeah.

348
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:49,160
They say the Grandmistress's death

349
00:31:49,240 --> 00:31:50,560
struck him hard,

350
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:52,720
and something went wrong
with the new Spirit Fire inside him.

351
00:31:52,800 --> 00:31:53,920
That's why he fell into a deep sleep.

352
00:31:54,440 --> 00:31:55,720
If she were still here,

353
00:31:55,800 --> 00:31:58,040
perhaps he would have awakened sooner.

354
00:31:58,560 --> 00:31:59,520
Yeah.

355
00:32:00,800 --> 00:32:01,880
Grandmaster.

356
00:32:03,320 --> 00:32:04,160
Tingyan.

357
00:32:06,800 --> 00:32:07,840
Grandmaster!

358
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:11,120
Grandmaster!

359
00:32:15,240 --> 00:32:16,280
Boss.

360
00:32:16,800 --> 00:32:18,040
Sima Jiao.

361
00:32:18,120 --> 00:32:19,600
Jiao. Jiao.

362
00:32:22,600 --> 00:32:25,000
Jiao! Come!

363
00:32:30,320 --> 00:32:31,360
Good morning, Jiao.

364
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:40,360
I told you,

365
00:32:41,440 --> 00:32:42,920
as long as I don't let you die,

366
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:45,920
you won't die.

367
00:32:53,920 --> 00:32:55,760
Your soul must still be here.

368
00:32:58,280 --> 00:32:59,600
I will find it.

369
00:33:06,360 --> 00:33:07,400
Take it slow.

370
00:33:20,680 --> 00:33:22,520
Master Yuan. How are things at the front?

371
00:33:22,600 --> 00:33:24,800
Hundreds of demon
soldiers have invaded the front line.

372
00:33:25,360 --> 00:33:26,480
They will soon reach here.

373
00:33:26,560 --> 00:33:29,160
Hundreds? Even with
the disciples from the reserve force,

374
00:33:29,240 --> 00:33:30,840
we only have a few dozen soldiers here.

375
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:35,400
Master Yuan, please place all
remaining forces under my command.

376
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:36,480
Together with Hei Nianjiu,

377
00:33:36,560 --> 00:33:38,760
I will defend
the Celestial Palace to the death.

378
00:33:38,840 --> 00:33:45,760
Defend the Celestial Palace to the death!

379
00:33:46,600 --> 00:33:47,640
Very well.

380
00:33:49,080 --> 00:33:50,040
We've cultivated for so long.

381
00:33:50,800 --> 00:33:53,200
If we die now
protecting the Celestial Palace,

382
00:33:53,720 --> 00:33:54,760
it will be a worthwhile death.

383
00:33:56,840 --> 00:33:58,960
- They're here.
- Everyone,

384
00:33:59,640 --> 00:34:01,920
- protect the Grandmaster!
- Yes, General!

385
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:49,159
The Spirit Fire? It's the Grandmaster.

386
00:34:51,440 --> 00:34:52,440
Did you really think I was dead?

387
00:35:07,640 --> 00:35:09,320
Greetings, Grandmaster!

388
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:10,920
Greetings, Grandmaster!

389
00:35:16,080 --> 00:35:16,920
Grandmaster.

390
00:35:18,120 --> 00:35:20,400
Grandmaster, you're awake.

391
00:35:26,840 --> 00:35:28,080
Why are you crying?

392
00:35:28,160 --> 00:35:31,400
Grandmaster, have
the two Spirit Fires in your body

393
00:35:32,040 --> 00:35:33,240
completely merged?

394
00:35:38,240 --> 00:35:39,280
Where's Tingyan?

395
00:35:40,400 --> 00:35:41,560
Have you found her?

396
00:35:42,080 --> 00:35:44,600
Grandmaster, have you forgotten?

397
00:35:46,760 --> 00:35:48,160
Tingyan left behind no fragments

398
00:35:49,280 --> 00:35:50,440
of her soul at all.

399
00:35:51,280 --> 00:35:53,120
She cannot be reborn.

400
00:35:54,160 --> 00:35:55,360
And Ruling

401
00:35:57,200 --> 00:35:58,240
met the same fate.

402
00:36:08,160 --> 00:36:09,200
What about the Shi clan?

403
00:36:10,400 --> 00:36:12,400
After the battle at Taiwei Mountain,

404
00:36:13,040 --> 00:36:14,680
the Shi clan was nearly annihilated.

405
00:36:15,600 --> 00:36:17,840
But we searched every
corner of the Celestial Palace

406
00:36:18,360 --> 00:36:20,120
and never found Shi Qianlv's body.

407
00:36:20,200 --> 00:36:22,440
I believe he must be
living under another name,

408
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:24,720
hiding somewhere in the Celestial Palace.

409
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:26,760
Having caused such upheaval,

410
00:36:28,520 --> 00:36:30,360
Shi Qianlv cannot remain here.

411
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:35,480
The breaches in the barrier

412
00:36:36,160 --> 00:36:37,920
were perfect for him to escape.

413
00:36:38,600 --> 00:36:39,560
Grandmaster, are you saying…?

414
00:36:40,440 --> 00:36:41,440
We'll go to the Demon Realm

415
00:36:42,760 --> 00:36:43,720
to root out the trouble.

416
00:36:44,680 --> 00:36:46,000
Grandmaster,

417
00:36:46,080 --> 00:36:48,160
though my medical skills are modest,

418
00:36:48,240 --> 00:36:50,200
I beg to accompany you

419
00:36:50,280 --> 00:36:52,000
to safeguard your health.

420
00:36:52,680 --> 00:36:55,000
Grandmaster, you have only just awakened.

421
00:36:55,080 --> 00:36:56,000
Are you sure about this?

422
00:36:58,360 --> 00:36:59,200
Do you object?

423
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:01,320
I wouldn't dare.

424
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:03,480
But I have one request.

425
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:05,880
During the Immortal-Demon War,

426
00:37:05,960 --> 00:37:08,160
many people of the Celestial Palace
were taken into the Demon Realm

427
00:37:08,240 --> 00:37:09,240
and went missing.

428
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:12,040
Grandmaster, I humbly ask

429
00:37:12,640 --> 00:37:14,600
that you build a refuge for them

430
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:17,320
within the Demon Realm

431
00:37:18,160 --> 00:37:19,880
if you encounter them there.

432
00:37:39,120 --> 00:37:40,640
I never intended to destroy this place.

433
00:37:42,280 --> 00:37:43,400
But in the end,

434
00:37:44,560 --> 00:37:46,280
this is what it has come to.

435
00:37:46,360 --> 00:37:48,120
This isn't your fault, Grandmaster.

436
00:37:48,640 --> 00:37:51,640
Back then, the Immortal-Demon Barrier
was suddenly destroyed.

437
00:37:51,720 --> 00:37:53,120
And after you fell into slumber,

438
00:37:53,200 --> 00:37:55,400
the Demon Lord set
his sights on our territory.

439
00:37:55,480 --> 00:37:57,040
That's why so many lives were lost.

440
00:38:08,440 --> 00:38:11,840
Grandmaster, did you just
mend the Immortal-Demon Barrier?

441
00:38:11,920 --> 00:38:13,480
The Grandmaster doesn't
seem as fearsome as the rumors say.

442
00:38:14,560 --> 00:38:17,160
The Grandmistress was
kind, gentle, and disliked bloodshed.

443
00:38:17,240 --> 00:38:18,880
It was because of her that he changed.

444
00:38:18,960 --> 00:38:20,400
What a pity that fate was so cruel.

445
00:38:32,040 --> 00:38:34,960
WHITE BONE ABYSS, DEMON REALM

446
00:38:39,480 --> 00:38:40,480
My lord.

447
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:44,360
Mingli, it has been centuries.

448
00:38:44,880 --> 00:38:46,800
When will I be reborn?

449
00:38:46,880 --> 00:38:47,720
My lord,

450
00:38:47,800 --> 00:38:50,000
in the Demon Realm, White Bone Abyss
holds the richest demonic energy.

451
00:38:50,600 --> 00:38:53,200
Please rest and recuperate here.
Don't worry, my lord.

452
00:38:53,880 --> 00:38:56,200
Everything is ready for
the restoration of your soul.

453
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:58,680
Now we only need
Sima Jiao's Fengshan blood.

454
00:38:59,440 --> 00:39:01,840
He's slept for 18 years.

455
00:39:01,920 --> 00:39:03,760
Eighteen years have passed,

456
00:39:03,840 --> 00:39:06,800
and you still haven't brought him to me?

457
00:39:07,720 --> 00:39:08,760
My lord,

458
00:39:08,840 --> 00:39:10,480
he has awakened recently,

459
00:39:11,040 --> 00:39:14,120
and he has even
successfully merged the two Spirit Fires.

460
00:39:14,200 --> 00:39:15,400
Useless fool!

461
00:39:18,160 --> 00:39:19,120
Please calm your anger, my lord.

462
00:39:19,640 --> 00:39:21,840
We still have the Frost Fish.
She can kill him and take his blood.

463
00:39:22,560 --> 00:39:26,120
You have searched for
her for so many years without success.

464
00:39:26,200 --> 00:39:28,280
She must already be dead.

465
00:39:28,360 --> 00:39:29,560
No,

466
00:39:29,640 --> 00:39:30,840
I'm sure she is still alive.

467
00:39:30,920 --> 00:39:32,800
The traces of her extreme-cold
nature left at the breaches

468
00:39:32,880 --> 00:39:34,000
of the Immortal-Demon Barrier

469
00:39:34,080 --> 00:39:35,240
were proof that she

470
00:39:35,320 --> 00:39:37,080
passed through
the barrier into the Demon Realm

471
00:39:37,160 --> 00:39:38,440
during the great disaster 18 years ago.

472
00:39:39,040 --> 00:39:40,080
But she

473
00:39:40,640 --> 00:39:42,240
must have been gravely injured,

474
00:39:42,320 --> 00:39:43,960
which is why we haven't
been able to track her down.

475
00:39:44,040 --> 00:39:47,400
There is only one Frost Fish in existence.

476
00:39:47,480 --> 00:39:49,840
She is the perfect
weapon to kill Sima Jiao.

477
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:52,840
You must find her.

478
00:39:52,920 --> 00:39:57,080
However, now that Sima Jiao
has two Spirit Fires within him,

479
00:39:57,160 --> 00:39:59,560
even with the Frost Fish,
we won't be able to kill him.

480
00:39:59,640 --> 00:40:03,040
We'll need the aid of
an ancient demonic artifact.

481
00:40:08,760 --> 00:40:12,040
Follow the map to find the Xingtian Chain.

482
00:40:12,120 --> 00:40:14,360
Once the Frost Fish
is refined into a froststone

483
00:40:14,440 --> 00:40:16,040
and set into the Xingtian Chain,

484
00:40:16,640 --> 00:40:18,360
Sima Jiao can be killed.

485
00:40:18,440 --> 00:40:21,400
Then you'll drain his blood
and provide the sacrifice I need.

486
00:40:22,440 --> 00:40:23,560
I will depart at once.

487
00:40:24,080 --> 00:40:26,560
Rest assured, my lord. I will
rally the strength of the entire clan

488
00:40:26,640 --> 00:40:28,200
to find that Frost Fish, Liao Tingyan.

489
00:40:30,600 --> 00:40:34,480
CELESTIAL CRANE CITY, DEMON REALM

490
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:38,760
CELESTIAL CRANE CITY

491
00:40:44,560 --> 00:40:45,560
Stop running!

492
00:40:47,520 --> 00:40:48,480
Hand it over!

493
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:51,600
- Pretty lady…
- Let go of me!

494
00:40:53,520 --> 00:40:55,240
- Please, have mercy.
- Out of the way!

495
00:40:58,000 --> 00:40:58,880
Eat.

496
00:41:04,480 --> 00:41:06,080
We're almost out of food again.

497
00:41:06,800 --> 00:41:08,240
After finishing this job,

498
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:10,440
I'll need to find more work.

499
00:41:11,240 --> 00:41:12,840
Winter City is far.

500
00:41:13,680 --> 00:41:15,080
Leave early and return early.

501
00:41:16,080 --> 00:41:18,040
Be careful on the road.

502
00:41:19,280 --> 00:41:22,160
- Don't get yourself hurt.
- I won't, Father.
